because data types store values,while def defines executable code.


| `def`                         | `float`                          |
| ----------------------------- | -------------------------------- |
| Used to **define a function** | Used to **store decimal values** |
| Creates a block of code       | Creates a variable               |
| Performs an action            | Holds data                       |


